    Checker Special type of actions which are called when there are no actions in the action que Checkers are responsible for actions like checking new messages in active/inactive group(s) Created by adam_ on 05-12-2017.

      • addCheckerWithTimeout

        public void addCheckerWithTimeout(Action checkerAction,
                                  long timeOutMs,
                                  boolean removeCheckerOnSuccess,
                                  Checker.CheckerResultCallback callback)
        Adds a checker action that that is returned after a timeout time, used to add temporary checker, used to add checker which are indented for one time action, or for limited time.
        Parameters:
        checkerAction - action to be added.
        timeOutMs - timeout time in milli seconds.
        removeCheckerOnSuccess - if true, checker is removed after action returns true.
        callback - callback called after the checker is removed.
